Achievements.Name: Playing it Safe
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on Easy.

Achievements.Description: Block an enemy attack by guarding.

Achievements.Description: Obtain something by closely examining an item.

Achievements.Name: Master of Unlocking
Achievements.Description: Use a lock pick to open something.

Achievements.Description: Use psychostimulants.

Achievements.Description: Increase your item slots.

Achievements.Description: Finish off an enemy with the knife.

Achievements.Description: Get ending 1.

Achievements.Name: Just A Memory Now
